			<p begin="4154567500t" end="4172927508t" region="region_00" tts:extent="57.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 79.29%" xml:id="subtitle260">That doesn't sound good,</p>
			<p begin="4154567500t" end="4172927508t" region="region_01" tts:extent="30.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 84.62%" xml:id="subtitle261">what is that?</p>
			<p begin="4173345008t" end="4190860006t" region="region_00" tts:extent="45.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="25.00% 79.29%" xml:id="subtitle262">95% of the Internet</p>
			<p begin="4173345008t" end="4190860006t" region="region_01" tts:extent="30.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="32.50% 84.62%" xml:id="subtitle263">isn't indexed</p>
