			<p begin="4249250003t" end="4265095000t" region="region_00" tts:extent="32.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="32.50% 79.29%" xml:id="subtitle270">Yeah, and now,</p>
			<p begin="4249250003t" end="4265095000t" region="region_01" tts:extent="35.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="30.00% 84.62%" xml:id="subtitle271">assassinations.</p>
			<p begin="4265512500t" end="4281785006t" region="region_00" tts:extent="65.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 79.29%" xml:id="subtitle272">Shouldn't we hand this over</p>
