			<p begin="4322242507t" end="4341010006t" region="region_00" tts:extent="50.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 84.62%" xml:id="subtitle276">That owl's on my leg.</p>
			<p begin="4341427506t" end="4358942503t" region="region_00" tts:extent="25.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="62.50% 79.29%" xml:id="subtitle277">(Patterson)</p>
