			<p begin="4688437502t" end="4710962506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="50.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="22.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle289">in their unmarked car</p>
			<p begin="4688437502t" end="4710962506t" region="region_01" tts:extent="55.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="20.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle290">by converging vehicles.</p>
			<p begin="4711380006t" end="4735565000t" region="region_00" tts:extent="65.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="17.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">No one could figure out how</p>
			<p begin="4711380006t" end="4735565000t" region="region_01" tts:extent="70.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="17.50% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle292">they coordinated the attacks.</p>
