			<p begin="4811897506t" end="4824820000t" region="region_00" tts:extent="57.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="30.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle301">TRAKZER's gone national.</p>
			<p begin="4825237500t" end="4841092506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="67.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="15.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle302">And the death toll's rising.</p>
