			<p begin="4841510006t" end="4856937501t" region="region_01" tts:extent="35.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="30.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle304">this down fast.</p>
			<p begin="4878627502t" end="4896142500t" region="region_00" tts:extent="52.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="22.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle305">Whoever wrote this app</p>
			<p begin="4878627502t" end="4896142500t" region="region_01" tts:extent="40.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="27.50% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle306">made it look like</p>
			<p begin="4896560001t" end="4916162500t" region="region_00" tts:extent="40.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="27.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle307">it's being hosted</p>
			<p begin="4896560001t" end="4916162500t" region="region_01" tts:extent="57.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="20.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle308">by a government network.</p>
			<p begin="4916580001t" end="4929095003t" region="region_00" tts:extent="35.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle309">Any attack that</p>
