			<p begin="4929512503t" end="4944940000t" region="region_00" tts:extent="37.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle311">would be hitting</p>
			<p begin="4929512503t" end="4944940000t" region="region_01" tts:extent="37.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle312">our own systems.</p>
