			<p begin="4957037501t" end="4972057506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="27.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="52.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">So, shutting</p>
			<p begin="4957037501t" end="4972057506t" region="region_01" tts:extent="35.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="52.50% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle315">this thing down</p>
			<p begin="4972475006t" end="4991242506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="52.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="32.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle316">is like trying to find</p>
			<p begin="4972475006t" end="4991242506t" region="region_01" tts:extent="55.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="32.50% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle317">a needle in a haystack.</p>
			<p begin="4991660006t" end="5017932502t" region="region_00" tts:extent="70.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle318">No, it's like finding a piece</p>
			<p begin="4991660006t" end="5017932502t" region="region_01" tts:extent="50.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle319">of hay in a haystack,</p>
			<p begin="5018350002t" end="5040040003t" region="region_00" tts:extent="25.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle320">like a very</p>
			<p begin="5018350002t" end="5040040003t" region="region_01" tts:extent="50.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle321">specific piece of hay</p>
			<p begin="5040457505t" end="5053390007t" region="region_00" tts:extent="37.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle322">in the haystack.</p>
			<p begin="5040457505t" end="5053390007t" region="region_01" tts:extent="10.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="77.50% 20.66%" xml:id="subtitle323">Yeah.</p>
			<p begin="5053807508t" end="5069235003t" region="region_00" tts:extent="25.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle324">Okay, well,</p>
			<p begin="5053807508t" end="5069235003t" region="region_01" tts:extent="45.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="10.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle325">you totally get it.</p>
			<p begin="5069652503t" end="5082167506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="10.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="77.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle326">Yeah.</p>
			<p begin="5082585006t" end="5094682508t" region="region_00" tts:extent="25.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="62.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle327">Actually...</p>
			<p begin="5095090000t" end="5122207506t" region="region_00" tts:extent="32.50% 5.33%" tts:origin="32.50% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle328">Wait a second,</p>
			<p begin="5095090000t" end="5122207506t" region="region_01" tts:extent="35.00% 5.33%" tts:origin="30.00% 15.33%" xml:id="subtitle329">I have an idea.</p>
